{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_07_01",
  "title": "川咲さくら 1話 瀕死の遊園地を救います！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんから聞いたんですけど、サニーピースに\n遊園地からオファーが来たって本当ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from Hashimoto-san that Sunny Peace\ngot an offer from an amusement park‚ is that true?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4333334048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "遊園地でライブするなんて楽しみです\n遊びに来たお客さんを笑顔にしちゃいますよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so excited to perform live at an amusement park!\nI'll make all the guests smile!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。乗り気になっているところ悪いが\nその仕事は断るつもりなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. It's too bad you were looking forward to it‚ but\nI'm going to decline that job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4535204284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、どうしてですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.353107357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "向こうが指定した日程に、サニピの五人を揃えるのは\nスケジュール的に無理なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's impossible to get all five members of Sunny Peace together\non the date they specified.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6345585505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "五人とも個人での仕事が増えてきて\n都合がつかなかったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's been getting more individual jobs lately\nso we couldn't make it work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4012252171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか……\nみんなで歌いたかったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so…?\nI wanted to sing with everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "先方も残念に思うはずだ。サニピのライブを\n遊園地を立て直すきっかけにしたいと言っていたからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure they'll be disappointed too. They said they wanted to use\nSunny Peace's concert as a springboard to revive the amusement park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6640825907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "立て直す……？\nもしかして、その遊園地は経営が苦しいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Revive…?\nDoes that mean that amusement park is struggling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "詳しくは分からないが\nお客さんの数が年々減っているのは事実らしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know the details but it seems that\nthe number of guests has been decreasing year by year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5913860956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、私達にオファーしたのは\nサニピのライブで遊園地を盛り上げるため……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then they offered us a job because they wanted to\nliven up the amusement park with Sunny Peace's live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3666690827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "サニーピースの明るさが\n今の遊園地に必要だと思ってくれたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They thought Sunny Peace's cheerfulness\nis what the amusement park needs right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0519037042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\nなんとかして、その遊園地でライブ出来ませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san\nIs there any way we can perform at that amusement park?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.200002416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "余程のことがない限りスケジュールは変えられないよ\nそれとも、どうしてもやりたい理由があるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't change the schedule unless something urgent comes up.\nOr is there a reason why you really want to do it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1437892802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "……私にとって遊園地は\n家族と笑顔で過ごした思い出の場所なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…For me‚ the amusement park\nis a place full of happy memories with my family.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.200002416,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "あんまり外で遊べなかったですし、たまに両親と\n遊園地に行くのが嬉しくて、いつもワクワクして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn't go out much‚ so going to the amusement park with my parents\nmade me so happy and excited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8537505245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "私みたいに、遊園地が大切な思い出の場所だって人は\nきっと沢山いるはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure there are lots of people who also cherish amusement parks\nas places of memories.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8333357494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "思い出の場所がなくなるのは寂しくて悲しいです！\n誰にもそんな思いはしてほしくありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's sad and lonely to see a place of memories disappear!\nI don't want anyone to feel that way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.8333377839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……さくらの熱意はよく分かった\nだがサニピの五人が揃うにはスケジュールが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… I understand your enthusiasm‚ Sakura\nbut to get all five Sunny Peace members together‚ the schedule…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6607988992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "五人全員が無理なら、私一人だけならどうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if it's just me instead of all five?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.5274655658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "さくら一人ならスケジュールは問題ないが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura alone wouldn't be a problem schedule-wise…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3484860418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "それなら私一人でライブをやります！\n寂れた遊園地を、私が立て直してみせますっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I'll do the live by myself!\nI'll revive that deserted amusement park!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2333377839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら。寂れたとか言うんじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey. Don't say it's deserted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.0200054484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ごめんなさい……えーと……\n瀕死の遊園地を、私が盛り上げてみせますっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I'm sorry… Uh…\nI'll revitalize that dying amusement park!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9000044506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら\n……仕方ないな。さくらの提案を先方に伝えてみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey…\n…It can't be helped. I'll relay your proposal to them‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0661277132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6327943799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.6327943799
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.6327943799
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "この間の遊園地の件だが\nさくらのソロライブが正式に決まったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About the amusement park‚\nyour solo live has been officially decided‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.5994610466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.5338801706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！　ありがとうございます！\n早速ライブに向けて準備を始めますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?! Thank you so much!\nI'll start preparing for the live right away!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9229687957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.6090591745
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "セトリを決めて、それから衣装を……\nそう言えば会場はどれくらいの広さなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll decide on the setlist‚ then the costumes…\nSpeaking of which‚ how big is the venue?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.3666711172,
      "sfxList": []
